quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,150,aur jab moose apni qoum mein nihayat ghusse aur afsos ki haalat mein wapas aeye. to kehnay lagey ke tum ne mere baad bohat hi bdatwari ki.kiya tum ne apne perwar-digaar ka hukum ( yani mera apne paas aana ) jald chaha ( yeh kaha ) aur ( shiddat ghazab se torat ki ) tkhtyan daal den aur apne bhai ke sir ( ke balon ) ko pakar kar apni taraf khenchnay lagey. unhon ne kaha ke bhai jaan log to mujhe kamzor samajte they aur qareeb tha ke qatal kar dein. to aisa kaam nah kiijiye ke dushman mujh par hansen aur mujhe zalim logon mein mat milaiyay
  7,151,tab unhon ne dua ki ke ae mere perwar-digaar mujhe aur mere bhai ko maaf farma aur hamein apni rehmat mein daakhil kar to sab se barh kar reham karne wala hai
  7,152,( khuda ne farmaya ke ) jin logon ne bichhre ko ( mabood ) bana liya tha un par perwar-digaar ka ghazab waqay hoga aur duniya ki zindagi mein zillat ( naseeb hogi ) aur hum iftira prdazon ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
  7,153,aur jinhon ne buray kaam kiye phir is ke baad tauba karli aur imaan le aeye to kuch shak nahi ke tumhara perwar-digaar is ke baad ( bakhash day ga ke woh ) bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  7,154,aur jab moose ka gussa faro howa to ( torat ) ki tkhtyan athalin aur jo kuch un mein likha tha woh un logon ke liye jo apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain. hadaayat aur rehmat thi
  7,155,aur moose ne is meyaad par jo hum ne muqarrar ki thi apni qoum ke sattar aadmi munhtakhib ( karkay koh tor par haazir ) tal kiye. jab un ko zalzalay ne pakra to moose ne kaha ke ae perwar-digaar to chahta to un ko aur mujh ko pehlay hi se halaak kar deta.kiya to is feal ki saza mein jo hum mein se be aqal logon nekiya hai hamein halaak kardey ga. yeh to teri azmaish hai. is se to jis ko chahay gumraah kere aur jis ko chahay hadaayat bakhshay. to hi hamara karsaaz hai to hamein ( hamaray gunah ) bakhash day aur hum par reham farma aur to sab se behtar bakhsnay wala hai
